{"tid":1147223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民既目標根本唔係臨時立法會，大家唔好搞錯同諗多！","createTime":"2019-05-09T17:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T14:19:55.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0e9558d428d4d1e7912e9fb0e6397a9e100a11","tid":1147223,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T17:28:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ke0KX5uICag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fke0KX5uICag&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=eedacc84\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ke0KX5uICag</a><br />\n<br />\n尾段今次幫返碌撚，<br />\n<br />\n合憲合法=合乎基本法<br />\n<br />\n而泛民由朝到晚都話星期六個會係合憲，要求政權承認佢個會議，者係堅持要體制內抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n但問題就係個會冇秘書處幫手，啲官又唔黎，政權根本唔會承認呢個係合法嘅會議，既然係咁就應該索性搞個臨時立法會，搞搞吓隨時再推去臨時政府，者係革命。<br />\n<br />\n但泛民都係跳唔出呢個框框，都係堅持係一國兩制底下抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n所以今次睇定啲好，<br />\n唔好將你哋想搞革命嘅主觀願望投射落涂謹申身上<br />\n佢哋嘅目標根本唔係臨時立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完美的誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca820edcb36037d297d15deff0a37d6743eb4738","tid":1147223,"uid":34334,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T17:32:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8be3e8e94cb4e56a4c32d9a62ba590476b8bd750","tid":1147223,"uid":19613,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑<br />\n<br />\n碌撚果個五區公投咪又係d 官無人理，技窮喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4134ef1c01a29